channel.title: 99 Firemaking
channel.description:
[center][b][size=15pt]My road to 99 firemaking[/size][/b][/center]
[s]Yes i know, what a stupid and easy skill to get up but to be honest im really only doing it for the cape, as i am not going for the firecape again until i get 80 range and i need a good cape to go with drag, oh and the fact i won 142k willows in a stake :) and realized that it will take only 142k willows for 99 firemaking :P[/s]
[b][u]Current level:[/u][/b] [b]58/99[/b]
[URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img488.imageshack.us/img488/4144/99firemakinggv6.jpg[/img][/URL]
Oh and this is mainly for a race aswel between me and a friend, who can get it first :P
I cbf with it atm ill carry on sooner or later
